7:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Feature Analysis"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"Both Fotor AI and Pixlr AI share a solid foundation of core features including Text To Image, Image To Image, Inpainting, Outpainting. Where Fotor AI pulls ahead is with exclusive access to Style Transfer, which can be a deciding factor for teams that rely on this capability. \n\nLooking at user ratings, Fotor AI holds an overall score of 5/10 and an ease of use score of 8/10, while Pixlr AI scores 5/10 overall and 7/10 for ease of use. These ratings reflect real user experiences and can indicate differences in usability, support quality, and overall satisfaction."}]]}]
8:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Pricing Breakdown"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"When it comes to pricing, both Fotor AI and Pixlr AI offer flexible pricing models. Both platforms offer free plans, which is great for testing before committing. Fotor AI's free tier and Pixlr AI's free tier each have their own limitations, so it is worth evaluating both to see which free offering better matches your initial needs."}]]}]
