b:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Who Should Choose Which?"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"The ideal user for each platform differs considerably. Fotor AI is best suited for photo editing, image enhancement, background removal, quick designs, making it a strong choice if you fall into any of these categories. Pixlr AI, meanwhile, shines for photo editing, quick fixes, background removal, browser editing, which means it may be the better pick if your needs align with those use cases.\n\nFounded in 2012, Fotor AI describes itself as \"AI-powered photo editor with image generation and enhancement.\" Pixlr AI, established in 2008, positions itself as \"Free browser-based AI photo editor with generation features.\" Both platforms have been in the market for a similar duration, giving each ample time to refine their offerings and build a loyal user base."}]]}]
c:["$","div",null,{"className":"verdict-box","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Our Verdict"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"After analyzing all the data, **Fotor AI** comes out slightly ahead in this comparison, thanks to more features (7 vs 6), availability of a free plan. However, this does not mean Pixlr AI is a poor choice — far from it. Pixlr AI excels in its own right, particularly for photo editing and quick fixes.\n\nOur recommendation: if you value combines ai generation with photo editing, go with Fotor AI. If fully browser-based, no install needed matters more to you, Pixlr AI is the way to go. Either way, both are solid platforms that have earned their place in the market."}]]}]
